554
00:52:07,711 --> 00:52:09,546
Made yourself some big bread.

555
00:52:09,671 --> 00:52:11,882
Now the Mafia wants to move in on you.

556
00:52:19,681 --> 00:52:20,599
So what?

557
00:52:20,724 --> 00:52:22,601
So, the Mafia grabbed your daughter.

558
00:52:23,143 --> 00:52:24,144
You knew it.

559
00:52:24,686 --> 00:52:26,355
You knew it when you hired me.

560
00:52:29,942 --> 00:52:30,692
Yeah.

561
00:52:31,568 --> 00:52:33,821
You tried to snatch one for a trade.

562
00:52:34,404 --> 00:52:36,615
But your flunky friends out there blew it.

563
00:52:37,199 --> 00:52:41,370
They burned some kid. Missed the man
we wanted to grab for a trade.

564
00:52:43,413 --> 00:52:45,290
Then you wanted to hustle old Shaft.

565
00:52:45,415 --> 00:52:48,752
I hired you for a job. I conned you,
but I never lied to you.

566
00:52:49,419 --> 00:52:50,838
My baby was grabbed.

567
00:52:51,421 --> 00:52:54,883
You'll get her back. You bought that deal.
