588
00:54:27,559 --> 00:54:28,519
Set a price.

589
00:54:33,774 --> 00:54:35,108
$10,000 a head.

590
00:54:37,778 --> 00:54:41,281
That's what the honky government
pays a cat in the Army for insurance.

591
00:54:42,324 --> 00:54:43,700
$10,000 a man.

592
00:54:45,911 --> 00:54:47,204
That's our price.

593
00:54:51,500 --> 00:54:52,501
All right.

594
00:54:57,381 --> 00:55:00,843
You telling me you're willing to lay out
that kind of bread for Marcy?

595
00:55:02,553 --> 00:55:03,971
Don't jive me, man.

596
00:55:04,972 --> 00:55:06,682
I can always get more money.

597
00:55:08,308 --> 00:55:09,601
I only got one baby.

598
00:55:10,602 --> 00:55:14,314
That means you already owe him $50,000
for the men he lost last night.

599
00:55:15,607 --> 00:55:16,650
All right.

600
00:55:19,069 --> 00:55:22,156
We can get a lot of brothers and sisters
out of jail with that.

601
00:55:22,239 --> 00:55:23,824
