607
00:55:39,464 --> 00:55:42,050
If he's worth $10,000, I'm worth $20,000.

608
00:55:44,011 --> 00:55:45,512
You got it, COD.

609
00:55:46,096 --> 00:55:48,056
Half now, half when I bring her home.

610
00:55:48,140 --> 00:55:48,974
All!

611
00:55:49,975 --> 00:55:50,893
Right now!

612
00:55:51,018 --> 00:55:53,729
Half, that's the best I'll do.

613
00:55:55,397 --> 00:55:57,107
