614
00:55:57,816 --> 00:55:59,359
Deliver the money tonight.

615
00:56:00,444 --> 00:56:02,738
I'll have my boys drop it off.

616
00:56:03,363 --> 00:56:07,576
At these prices, you blow it, Shaft,
I'm not gonna like it.

617
00:56:07,784 --> 00:56:09,453
Not even a little bit.

618
00:56:09,703 --> 00:56:13,749
I thought the money didn't matter to you.
Just getting your baby back.

619
00:56:16,793 --> 00:56:18,587
Money always matters.

620
00:56:32,142 --> 00:56:34,061
This is where I get off, man.

621
00:56:34,812 --> 00:56:39,066
One thing we got to get straight.
If it comes to a fight, we do it my way.

622
00:56:40,150 --> 00:56:42,444
For that kind of bread, the brothers'll play.

623
00:56:42,528 --> 00:56:44,696
As long as you remember
we owe them five.

624
00:56:44,780 --> 00:56:45,948
I said, my way!

625
00:56:48,534 --> 00:56:49,701
I'll call you.

626
00:57:22,860 --> 00:57:25,028
- Hey, man!
- Hey, Billy? Come here.

627
00:57:26,280 --> 00:57:27,781
- Do me a favor.
- Sure.

628
00:57:27,906 --> 00:57:32,035
- Go up to my place and turn on the...
- Hey, no, man. I've already turned on.

629
00:57:32,369 --> 00:57:34,121
No, Billy, turn on the lights.

630
00:57:34,246 --> 00:57:35,122
Lights.

631
00:57:35,205 --> 00:57:37,166
- About two minutes, okay?
- Got it.

632
00:58:32,179 --> 00:58:33,889
How are we doing, love?

633
00:58:35,224 --> 00:58:37,309
That's nice. Don't make any trouble.

634
00:58:38,352 --> 00:58:40,604
- Johnny!
- What do you say, Rollie?

635
00:58:41,021 --> 00:58:42,815
Gorgeous coat!

636
00:58:45,192 --> 00:58:48,195
How about letting me
take over the bar for a while?

637
00:58:48,278 --> 00:58:50,864
There's nothing I wouldn't do for $20.

638
00:58:56,578 --> 00:58:57,830
Have funzies.

639
00:59:23,730 --> 00:59:24,857
You look ready.

640
00:59:25,440 --> 00:59:27,860
Yeah, okay. Scotch and water, both.

641
00:59:33,240 --> 00:59:34,658
On the house, gents.

642
00:59:40,330 --> 00:59:43,125
And since the house is buying,
I'll have one.

643
00:59:51,133 --> 00:59:53,594
To the big-hearted owner
of the No Name Bar.

644
00:59:53,677 --> 00:59:55,888
Whether he knows he's generous or not.

645
01:00:02,311 --> 01:00:03,437
That's all booze!

646
01:00:03,562 --> 01:00:04,563
Right on.

647
01:00:05,063 --> 01:00:07,774
All booze. One zillion percent.

648
01:00:20,162 --> 01:00:21,330
Hold on.

649
01:00:25,083 --> 01:00:26,210
Hold on.

