01:02:16,862 --> 01:02:18,697
Vic, private line.

667
01:02:22,618 --> 01:02:23,744
Hey, sweet baby?

668
01:02:23,869 --> 01:02:25,454
This is your lover man.

669
01:02:26,538 --> 01:02:28,165
Who the hell is this?

670
01:02:28,999 --> 01:02:30,501
Two sweet guesses.

671
01:02:32,628 --> 01:02:33,879
