01:02:55,901 --> 01:02:57,110
About two.

680
01:02:58,403 --> 01:03:00,906
I'll close up and we'll go over to my pad.

681
01:03:01,740 --> 01:03:04,409
You walk in that front door,
I'll close up right now.

682
01:03:06,662 --> 01:03:10,541
- I'll have a car there in a few seconds.
- That's what I want to hear.

683
01:03:19,299 --> 01:03:21,134
A lot of loose stuff around here?

684
01:03:24,596 --> 01:03:26,598
All a man can handle, deacon.

685
01:03:31,603 --> 01:03:33,230
What are you looking at?

686
01:03:37,818 --> 01:03:38,986
Get lost.

687
01:03:42,322 --> 01:03:43,782
Go do something.

688
01:03:45,617 --> 01:03:47,161
Where are my manners?

689
01:03:47,995 --> 01:03:50,455
I didn't even introduce myself
to you gentlemen.

690
01:03:52,124 --> 01:03:54,585
My name is John Shaft.

691
01:03:55,502 --> 01:03:56,545
Freeze!

692
01:04:13,937 --> 01:04:15,397
Throw me a towel.

693
01:04:16,273 --> 01:04:19,109
