licenses to carry them.

700
01:05:27,636 --> 01:05:30,222
"Jewelry couriers," the licenses say.

701
01:05:30,848 --> 01:05:32,349
Detroit people.

702
01:05:34,726 --> 01:05:36,979
- Will you turn them loose?
- I have no choice.

703
01:05:38,063 --> 01:05:39,815
They'll leave town.

704
01:05:39,898 --> 01:05:42,734
You'll have strangers looking for you,
not them.

705
01:05:43,694 --> 01:05:45,571
Can I have a private talk with them?

706
01:05:46,697 --> 01:05:49,700
What you'll do to poor Carmen now?
Give him cancer?

707
01:05:50,993 --> 01:05:52,953
You busted his head, settle.

708
01:05:54,788 --> 01:05:57,499
