738
01:09:19,409 --> 01:09:21,203
- Know where it is?
- I'll find it.

739
01:09:21,453 --> 01:09:23,747
12:30. Five minutes late would be too late.

740
01:09:23,831 --> 01:09:25,666
I'll be there. 'Bye.

741
01:10:08,250 --> 01:10:09,918
It's Vic Androzzi.

