749
01:11:01,512 --> 01:11:04,556
It's that big-eared Captain I got
who was listening.

750
01:11:07,726 --> 01:11:10,479
He thinks he heard you discussing
a kidnapping.

751
01:11:12,689 --> 01:11:14,733
He thinks the Mafia's involved.

752
01:11:17,820 --> 01:11:19,947
And he knows Bumpy Jonas is involved.

753
01:11:20,280 --> 01:11:21,782
Tell him to ask Bumpy then.

