877
01:26:30,691 --> 01:26:32,901
All right, where are the uniforms?

878
01:26:52,880 --> 01:26:55,507
- Who's that?
- The night janitor. He's okay.

879
01:26:56,383 --> 01:26:59,136
Use him to find out
which room they got her in.

880
01:27:00,929 --> 01:27:03,348
- Getting it together?
- Yeah, right on.

881
01:27:14,776 --> 01:27:15,944
Beautiful.

882
01:27:24,620 --> 01:27:25,913
Just beautiful.

883
01:27:27,789 --> 01:27:29,541
Jerry, how are you doing, baby?

884
01:27:33,837 --> 01:27:34,963
Hey, boy?

885
01:27:39,843 --> 01:27:41,887
Send up two coffees and a Coke.

886
01:27:43,138 --> 01:27:44,556
Glass or a straw?

887
01:27:45,891 --> 01:27:47,142
For the Coke.

888
01:27:47,476 --> 01:27:48,852
Make it a straw.

889
01:27:53,106 --> 01:27:54,107
Straw?

890
01:27:54,733 --> 01:27:56,318
You heard me, straw.

891
01:27:58,403 --> 01:27:59,863
Right.

892
01:28:02,533 --> 01:28:04,159
You're a shrewd cat, Shaft.

893
01:28:04,243 --> 01:28:07,246
You and your boys blow it
and I'll be one dead cat!

894
01:28:07,871 --> 01:28:10,457
You all know the plan. No mistakes.

895
01:28:12,417 --> 01:28:13,502
Let's go.

896
01:28:47,995 --> 01:28:51,039
There you are, sir.
Two coffees, a Coke and a straw.

897
01:28:51,290 --> 01:28:53,250
- Want me to take it in?
- Whoa.

898
01:28:56,545 --> 01:28:57,546
Right.

899
01:29:04,970 --> 01:29:06,388
Hey, thank you!

900
01:29:07,973 --> 01:29:09,766
- I'll be seeing you.
- Okay.

901
01:30:16,834 --> 01:30:17,918
Shut up!

902
01:30:22,089 --> 01:30:24,424
- What do you guys want?
- Your coat.

903
01:30:53,912 --> 01:30:55,330
Rope and harness.

904
01:31:12,764 --> 01:31:14,016
Go ahead down.

905
01:31:47,299 --> 01:31:48,926
Did you hear anything?

906
01:33:17,139 --> 01:33:19,349
This damn thing won't burn hot enough.

907
01:33:19,433 --> 01:33:22,102
You got something else
in there that'll burn?

908
01:33:38,869 --> 01:33:40,120
It's gin, man.

909
01:33:45,042 --> 01:33:46,502
What else you got?

910
01:33:50,672 --> 01:33:51,757
Gasoline.

911
01:34:03,018 --> 01:34:04,061
Come on!

912
01:34:36,135 --> 01:34:37,678
Give me a cigarette.

913
01:34:48,814 --> 01:34:50,732
- You know what to do?
- Yeah.

914
01:37:24,219 --> 01:37:26,054
Let's get out of here!

915
01:37:52,706 --> 01:37:53,749
Come on!

916
01:37:55,292 --> 01:37:56,376
Let's go!

917
01:38:48,428 --> 01:38:49,721
Androzzi, here.

918
01:38:50,430 --> 01:38:53,642
- Vic, your case just busted wide open.
